  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5096093">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5096093/" class="title-link">好看，耐看</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5096093"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/39644558/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/39644558/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">霍比特人</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-09-13"
      class="main-meta">2011-09-13 20:15:13</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5096093_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这本书从不同角度来描述20世纪的空战，看法犀利，而且有非常深刻。让我们对空军有了深刻的理解，能看清军事发展的脉络。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
